{"tid":343891,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅白背心濕透黑色內在美現形","createTime":"2017-08-02T00:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T03:34:39.000Z","uid":81228,"like":101,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a4b6a041fafc7bb458ed35d45f6d9602c79c71","tid":343891,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T00:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d17ixjpazu3j94.cloudfront.net/images/2017/07/30/150139958446740hCv59pMD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd17ixjpazu3j94.cloudfront.net%2Fimages%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F150139958446740hCv59pMD0.jpg&h=6f124fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲（圖／hyunah_aa Instagram、topstarnews）<br />\n<br />\n有如「小野馬」一般的25歲韓星泫雅，自出道以來性感妖艷的魔鬼身材就一直備受討論，只要一出場必能瞬間擄獲全場粉絲的心。前天（29日），她受邀參加首爾蠶室舉辦的「Water Bomb Festival」，只見身穿白色背心和牛仔短褲的她，被粉絲用水槍噴得全身濕答答，黑色的內在美若隱若現，讓在場民眾都瘋狂暴動！<br />\n<br />\n▼（圖／topstarnews）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2017/07/30/15013997064209uwR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F15013997064209uwR6.jpg&h=80f584ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2017/07/30/15013997400265ZYqk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F15013997400265ZYqk.jpg&h=be502de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泫雅前天出席南韓雪碧的水槍節活動，一上台就是連唱好幾首夯曲，勁歌熱舞的過程中還頻頻被粉絲拿水槍噴射，眼看身穿白色低胸背心、牛仔短褲、細高跟鞋的她，S型性感曲線及超白美腿表露無遺，就像經歷了一場大雨般，從頭到腳全身濕漉漉。<br />\n<br />\n▼（圖／mydaily）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2017/07/30/15013997842112dyEW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F15013997842112dyEW.jpg&h=b68bc685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2017/07/30/15013998037031nLCp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F15013998037031nLCp.jpg&h=0e8bee7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過，更讓人害羞的是，濕透的白色背心竟透出了她的黑色胸罩，豐滿的上圍呼之欲出，更露出了傲人的事業線，最後她索性脫下高跟鞋瘋狂熱舞，以性感舞姿著稱的她，抖胸、開腿等各種挑逗的舞姿都不吝嗇地展現給大家，把現場氣氛炒到最高點，讓粉絲的眼睛都大吃冰淇淋，嗨爆全場。<br />\n<br />\n▼（圖／OSEN）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2017/07/30/15013996695154sgIn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F15013996695154sgIn.jpg&h=672ed196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼（圖／bnt）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2017/07/30/1501399760292ur2J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F1501399760292ur2J.jpg&h=0cf7d38b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=72706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2Fnews.php%3Fnid%3D72706&d=TVDa0LtBSmyBeoC%2BwxTZ74zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5b2d1c6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=72706</a>"},{"pid":"099b726d0ca4bbf4d1d971577a9e8931c0342798","tid":343891,"uid":18456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T00:10:14.000Z","msg":"不得了不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d2c25444d4381df9ed58490e1b5616565e09e4","tid":343891,"uid":25101,"like":83,"dislike":10,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T00:27:17.000Z","msg":"韓國妓女文化"},{"pid":"374ed129b227606e8de4bf92f0407cd6e3040624","tid":343891,"uid":129176,"like":46,"dislike":6,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T00:32:15.000Z","msg":"假波 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84accaa4a8e07e77e27cfd0433a263cba4c118e","tid":343891,"uid":22553,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T00:41:21.000Z","msg":"個樣整到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe9ebee2814ba25176848e77f7a75b8df79a3ec","tid":343891,"uid":81